      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for exceptional volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained for structural integrity, featuring reinforced subframe mounts and a suspension geometry that retains its original communicative feedback. This is a mechanically sound example, offering the raw, naturally aspirated performance and precise throttle response that defines the golden era of the M division.",
